{"tid":1164970,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾舜晞爆紅被質疑整容？忠粉翻舊照「力撐」偶像","createTime":"2019-05-21T12:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T14:16:46.000Z","uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0669fdab174b50be1c64e5623cd38665a027cb14","tid":1164970,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"張狗真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《倚天屠龍記》在無綫熱播，劇中一班新紮小生花旦引起網友，當中飾演張無忌的曾舜晞，有不少網友對他的美貎充滿了問號，人紅新聞多，有不少網友找回他昔日讀書時候的照片，其中一張簡直判若兩人，面部浮腫、鼻子亦沒有現在這樣筆直，不過亦有曾舜晞支持者，提出反証，上載了不少他中學時的相片，相中人的曾舜晞充滿稚氣，但輪廓標緻，已經是校草級數，不過被質疑整容，換個角度來看，是人氣的指標，你紅了，網友才有興趣搜尋你的一切。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2758282/org/ef57fb6756efd9fb9fe6ed70e864c254.jpg/PEboB4EkjO41Kky5XOzOGkCWw-Kar6yjJhlKlSYZSpU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2758282%2Forg%2Fef57fb6756efd9fb9fe6ed70e864c254.jpg%2FPEboB4EkjO41Kky5XOzOGkCWw-Kar6yjJhlKlSYZSpU&h=b759717e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2758280/org/649f31795e89f8d12e7b951397828ae9.jpg/IL0fMJ2Kz1JzO5DnQpbQrNL8YYduB3B2TgIrOk4CKzo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2758280%2Forg%2F649f31795e89f8d12e7b951397828ae9.jpg%2FIL0fMJ2Kz1JzO5DnQpbQrNL8YYduB3B2TgIrOk4CKzo&h=192d9ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2758283/org/563e92c4eb5f31b77fc4bef5c21e76a8.jpg/8FZv1L8I1hwB4ujG8UMm430a7R7e4r8BojKKP6Iyij8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2758283%2Forg%2F563e92c4eb5f31b77fc4bef5c21e76a8.jpg%2F8FZv1L8I1hwB4ujG8UMm430a7R7e4r8BojKKP6Iyij8&h=9c686b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2758281/org/9d56552afb3a010eaf97456b3a538347.jpg/YEZFQsLsECjjS1WTMHJx1eizr4edvzyCIENZSy